@host = http://localhost:5000

### Create a generated short link
POST {{host}}/api/links
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://github.com/features/copilot"
}

### Create a custom short link
POST {{host}}/api/links
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/",
  "customCode": "dotnet"
}

### Follow a short link
GET {{host}}/dotnet

### Read one link's stats
GET {{host}}/api/links/dotnet/stats

### List all links
GET {{host}}/api/links
